Patrick Malahide https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Malahide 0 Patrick Gerald Duggan (born on 24 March 1945), known professionally as Patrick Malahide, is a British actor, known for his roles as Detective Sergeant Albert Chisholm in the TV series Minder and Balon Greyjoy in the TV series Game of Thrones.
